and '50s and through the '60s

00:14:21.070 --> 00:14:24.460
and even today, it's one of his
most often performed pieces.

00:14:24.460 --> 00:14:26.660
There are a couple of reasons
why people are less familiar

00:14:26.660 --> 00:14:28.160
with the 13 instrument version.

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:34.130
One is, while Martha was alive, she
died in 1991, Copland stipulated

00:14:34.130 --> 00:14:37.540
that nobody but Martha could
play the ballet version.

00:14:37.540 --> 00:14:42.070
And there's a funny story behind
that which is when she died

00:14:42.070 --> 00:14:44.740
