have parts to it and they called

00:14:53.410 --> 00:14:58.490
up the Graham Company and said, "I
know you have parts which you paid

00:14:58.490 --> 00:15:01.410
for and made but technically,
they're our property,"

00:15:01.410 --> 00:15:02.790
because they hold the copyright.

00:15:02.790 --> 00:15:05.050
