was doing at that time.

00:15:26.310 --> 00:15:28.170
It sounds like "Rodeo"
and "Billy the Kid".

00:15:28.170 --> 00:15:32.420
It's very much of that time period
and the same use of the orchestra.

00:15:32.420 --> 00:15:36.510
It wasn't until the late '60s that
some friends of his convinced him

00:15:36.510 --> 00:15:39.780
that people wanted to hear at
least the chamber orchestration

00:15:39.780 --> 00:15:41.730
