lift to the dancer so that you all

00:51:19.400 --> 00:51:20.880
in the audience can enjoy it.

00:51:20.880 --> 00:51:23.820
So, what makes my life
easier is knowing as much

00:51:23.820 --> 00:51:27.100
as knowing a brain dump from the
choreographer, what's on his mind?

00:51:27.100 --> 00:51:28.400
