00:54:54.510 --> 00:54:56.310
&gt;&gt; Aaron Sherber: Right.

00:54:56.310 --> 00:54:59.040
[ Inaudible Remark ]

00:54:59.040 --> 00:55:00.340
&gt;&gt; Aaron Sherber: Yes.

